odule, so `Class.forName(\"org.xml.sax.helpers.SecuritySupport\")` does not find the `xmlParserAPIs` copy from the normal test classpath.\n\nChange made:\n- Updated `OrgXmlSaxHelpersSecuritySupportTest` to match the existing pattern used by the other `xmlParserAPIs` tests:\n  - first try normal `Class.forName`\n  - if that fails, locate the `xmlParserAPIs-*.jar`\n  - load the class through an isolated `URLClassLoader`\n  - close the loader after each test\n  - catch Native Image unsupported dynamic-class-loading errors using `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError`\n\nUpdated file:\n- `tests/src/xerces/xmlParserAPIs/2.6.2/src/test/java/xerces/xmlParserAPIs/OrgXmlSaxHelpersSecuritySupportTest.java`\n\nI did not run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_015711222997be9e0169f8d72479f8819c87374bf88bbe0bf5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1922, "output": 739, "cacheRead": 31744, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34405, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777915672916, "responseId": "resp_015711222997be9e0169f8d719af90819c992563e2080a96b2"}}
